modName: Whispers in the Dark Quest Fix
summary: Can\'t get contracts from Nazir after Astrid tells you to do so, preventing you from progressing in the Dark Brotherhood main quest? This should fix that
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/images/11361-2-1330277534.jpg[/img][/center]

This esp should fix the quest Whispers in the Dark for the Dark Brotherhood, where Nazir will not display the dialog to get the needed contracts to progress the quest.
author: Ares1
